201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne finished with a long supplication.\u201d The man said, \u201cWhich charity is best?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cGreat effort with little means.\u201d The man said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19499,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/15\/umar-dua-qunut\/","url_meta":{"origin":36702,"position":1},"title":"Umar on Qunut: Supplication of Umar during persecution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 15, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ubaid ibn Umair reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, supplicated after bowing in prayer and he said, \u201cO Allah, forgive the believing men and believing women and the Muslim men and Muslim women, bring their hearts together and reconcile between them, support them against Your enemies\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2041,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/04\/dua-witr-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":36702,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Qunut: Supplication for performing Witr prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Hasan ibn Ali reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, taught me some words to say in the Witr prayer, \u201cO Allah, guide me among those You have guided, secure me among those You have secured, protect me among those You have protected, bless me in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33020,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/prophets-dua-after-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":36702,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet\u2019s supplication after finishing prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Mughirah ibn Shu\u2019bah reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, finished the prayer and invoked peace, he would say, \u201cThere is no God but Allah, alone without partner. To him belongs the dominion, all praise, and he has power over all things. O Allah, none\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25901,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/02\/05\/dua-wake-up-in-night\/","url_meta":{"origin":36702,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication to say when waking up in night","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 5, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever wakes up in the night and says, 'There is no God but Allah, alone without any partner. To Him belong the dominion and all praise, and He has power over all things. All praise is due\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11462,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/17\/prophet-protects-woman-from-husband\/","url_meta":{"origin":36702,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Divorce: The Prophet protects wife from abusive husband","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 17, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The wife of Al-Walid ibn 'Uqbah came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and she complained to him saying, \u201cO Messenger of Allah! Al-Walid has beaten me!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cSay to him: He has protected me.\u201d She did not stay but\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/36702","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=36702"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/36702\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=36702"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"hr